            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1325,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01UjEqbwsW2HMXuYTRAmyLDZ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01DpemwGhqkRa2VykZS33wUa\",\"name\":\"extract-1\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I want to dig deeper into your audience to make sure we nail the marketing angle. You mentioned podcast hosts with large audiences who want guests that fit their show—but let me ask you this:\",\"examples\":[\"What specific pain points do they experience RIGHT NOW when finding guests? (e.g., wasting time, getting irrelevant pitches, difficulty vetting quality, etc.)\",\"What does 'large audience' mean to you? (e.g., 10k+ downloads per episode, 50k+ listeners, etc.)\",\"Beyond just 'fit'—what else matters to them? (e.g., guest credibility, audience overlap, production quality, availability, etc.)\",\"What's their biggest frustration with current solutions or methods they use today?\"],\"conclusion\":\"Help me understand the real, specific pain points and desires of your ideal podcast host so we can craft messaging that truly resonates with them.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2710,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":257,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
