            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2086,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01EctEbNJhCsfZpuw7RXb2La\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01X4tzeYK9FtdaQcfXhPjW4E\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"output\":[{\"topic\":\"idea\",\"summary\":\"Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service that connects podcast hosts with quality guests at scale. The platform solves the \\\"needle in a haystack\\\" problem by using AI-powered filtering to help hosts find great content in minutes instead of hours. The service helps both hosts (who get great content) and guests (who get exposure), and is the only platform doing this at scale.\"},{\"topic\":\"audience\",\"summary\":\"Target audience is podcast hosts with large audiences. Their main pain points are: (1) spending hours finding guests that are a good fit for their show, and (2) being bombarded with messages from low-quality, spammy guests who don't add value to their shows. They want to find guests that align with their show's content and audience.\"},{\"topic\":\"solution\",\"summary\":\"Friend of the Pod offers 100+ filters to find the perfect guest for a show. The platform uses AI to match hosts and guests based on their content, audience, and goals. What differentiates the solution is proprietary AI models trained on messages that successful podcast hosts receive, which filters out pitches predicted to not be a good fit for the show.\"},{\"topic\":\"socialProof\",\"summary\":\"Over 10,000 creators use Friend of the Pod to find guests for their shows. Real case study: A host found 3 quality guests in 10 minutes instead of 5 hours of manual outreach, which led to 2 viral episodes. Founder credibility: The founder previously worked at Spotify and Apple Podcasts, giving them firsthand industry experience and deep understanding of what makes a guest a good fit for a show.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2161,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":437,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
