            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1126,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Kvm12KaDCF28jvKSJ96yXj\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_013dUidc6DEjQRGufV9Rn7K1\",\"name\":\"extract-2\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"Amazing work! You've given me everything I need to create a compelling landing page for Friend of the Pod. Now you have two options:\",\"examples\":[\"**Personalize the design (optional):** Upload your logo, pick your brand colors, add social links, or choose specific images. Check out the Brand Personalization panel on the left. This takes just a few minutes and makes your page feel uniquely yours.\",\"**Build right away:** Skip personalization for now and hit 'Build My Site' to see your page come to life. You can always customize colors, logos, and images later!\"],\"conclusion\":\"Both paths work great—it's totally up to you. What feels right?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":21819,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":208,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
