            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01M2QdpWHZSU6z6V1ey1yRSq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01TjaSKoKEfJbid8WzQabs5i\",\"name\":\"extract-5\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"Great! So you're connecting podcasters with each other. I need to dig deeper to understand what makes Friend of the Pod special and worth building a landing page around.\\n\\nLet me ask you this: **What specific problem are you solving for podcasters?** \\n\\nAre you helping:\\n- Podcasters find guests for their shows?\\n- Podcasters find collaboration opportunities?\\n- New podcasters find established ones to learn from?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\nAnd **what makes your matchmaking service different** from just posting in Facebook groups or using existing podcast networks?\",\"examples\":[\"We match guest experts with podcasters who need them, using AI to find the perfect fit based on audience alignment\",\"We help solo podcasters find co-hosts or collaborators to grow their audience together\",\"We connect niche podcasters in the same space so they can cross-promote and build community\"],\"conclusion\":\"Help me understand the core problem you're solving and what makes your approach unique.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2306,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":268,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
