            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01AzuSfTQ1ShPnsa6HRxUqvL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01BQpCVu42AYAZTUCUVTUm5h\",\"name\":\"extract-16\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I love that you're building a program specifically designed for this audience! But I need to understand the specifics of HOW your program solves their problems. \\n\\nYou mentioned your clients face two major obstacles:\\n1. **Psychological barrier** - They've been told they're too old to get fit\\n2. **Lack of experience** - Many have never been active before\\n\\nSo tell me: What specific features, methods, or approaches does your program use to overcome these barriers? How do you help them break through the \\\"I'm too old\\\" mindset? How do you make it work for complete beginners?\",\"examples\":[\"We use modified exercises that prove age is just a number, combined with motivational coaching that rebuilds their confidence\",\"We start with foundational movements and gradually progress, so beginners never feel overwhelmed or out of place\",\"We focus on functional fitness that helps them with everyday activities, so they see real-world results immediately\"],\"conclusion\":\"What makes your program different and specifically effective for men in their 50s with no fitness experience?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2972,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":287,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
