            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01H48wBets1bpphJU1R9P7kW\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_016bEGnTJEfiweBRryJwUnAN\",\"name\":\"extract-17\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"Great! So your solution focuses on bodyweight exercises and injury prevention. But I want to make sure we capture the FULL power of what you're offering.\\n\\nYou've told me WHAT you do (bodyweight exercises, injury prevention), but I need to understand the deeper impact. Let me ask you this:\\n\\n**How does this specifically address the two pain points your clients face?**\\n\\n1. **The \\\"I'm too old\\\" mindset** - How do bodyweight exercises and injury prevention help them overcome this psychological barrier? What results or confidence do they gain?\\n\\n2. **The beginner experience** - Why is bodyweight training + injury prevention the RIGHT approach for someone who's never been active? What makes them feel capable and successful?\\n\\nIn other words: What transformation or outcome do your clients experience? What can they DO or FEEL after working with you that they couldn't before?\",\"examples\":[\"They realize they can do real strength training without needing a gym, which removes the intimidation factor and proves age doesn't matter\",\"They build strength safely without joint pain, so they actually stick with it and see results instead of getting injured and quitting\",\"They gain confidence through small wins with bodyweight movements, which rebuilds their belief that they CAN get fit\"],\"conclusion\":\"What's the real transformation or benefit your clients experience from your bodyweight + injury prevention approach?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3587,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":352,\"service_tier