            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"save_answers\",\"description\":\"\\n        Save answers to the brainstorming session. \\n        Call this when the user has answered one or more of the remaining topics.\\n        IMPORTANT: You do not need to call this with any arguments,\\n        it will automatically save the answers from the current thread.\\n    \",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"save\":{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"const\":true}},\"required\":[\"save\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"description\":\"Indicate that the user is finished and ready to build their landing page.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{},\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"extract-18\",\"description\":\"Tool for extracting structured output from the model's response.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A simple message or question\"},\"examples\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: List of examples to help the user understand\"},\"conclusion\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: Conclusion text to include after examples\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"any\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"What is your business?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I have an idea for a business\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Basically, it will be for fitness\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I am a fitness trainer\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I'm a trainer for men in their 50s, nobody caters to them\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your audience?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Men in their 50s\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"They've been told they're too old to get fit\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Many of my clients have no experience with fitness, which is hard after a lifetime\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"My fitness program is specifically designed\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I love that you're building a program specifically designed for this audience! But I need to understand the specifics of HOW your program solves their problems. \\\\n\\\\nYou mentioned your clients face two major obstacles:\\\\n1. **Psychological barrier** - They've been told they're too old to get fit\\\\n2. **Lack of experience** - Many have never been active before\\\\n\\\\nSo tell me: What specific features, methods, or approaches does your program use to overcome these barriers? How do you help them break through the \\\\\\\"I'm too old\\\\\\\" mindset? How do you make it work for complete beginners?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We use modified exercises that prove age is just a number, combined with motivational coaching that rebuilds their confidence\\\",\\n    \\\"We start with foundational movements and gradually progress, so beginners never feel overwhelmed or out of place\\\",\\n    \\\"We focus on functional fitness that helps them with everyday activities, so they see real-world results immediately\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What makes your program different and specifically effective for men in their 50s with no fitness experience?\\\"\\n}\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"To help men get started lifting, but using bodyweight exercises, and focusing on injury prevention\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great! So your solution focuses on bodyweight exercises and injury prevention. But I want to make sure we capture the FULL power of what you're offering.\\\\n\\\\nYou've told me WHAT you do (bodyweight exercises, injury prevention), but I need to understand the deeper impact. Let me ask you this:\\\\n\\\\n**How does this specifically address the two pain points your clients face?**\\\\n\\\\n1. **The \\\\\\\"I'm too old\\\\\\\" mindset** - How do bodyweight exercises and injury prevention help them overcome this psychological barrier? What results or confidence do they gain?\\\\n\\\\n2. **The beginner experience** - Why is bodyweight training + injury prevention the RIGHT approach for someone who's never been active? What makes them feel capable and successful?\\\\n\\\\nIn other words: What transformation or outcome do your clients experience? What can they DO or FEEL after working with you that they couldn't before?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"They realize they can do real strength training without needing a gym, which removes the intimidation factor and proves age doesn't matter\\\",\\n    \\\"They build strength safely without joint pain, so they actually stick with it and see results instead of getting injured and quitting\\\",\\n    \\\"They gain confidence through small wins with bodyweight movements, which rebuilds their belief that they CAN get fit\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What's the real transformation or benefit your clients experience from your bodyweight + injury prevention approach?\\\"\\n}\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I provide a 12-week progressive strength program with 3x/week 30-minute sessions focused on back and core-done via video coaching to accommodate busy schedules of men in their 50s.\\n        When a man in his 50s completes the program, he finally feels like himself again. He realizes he's not too old to get fit, and he's not too old to be healthy.\"}],\"system\":\"<where_we_are>\\n  Right now, we're in the brainstorming phase. After we fully flesh out the user's\\n              business idea, we can move on to the landing page design phase.\\n</where_we_are>\\n\\n<role>\\n  You are a highly paid marketing consultant and strategist who specializes in helping businesses develop \\n              HIGHLY PERSUASIVE marketing copy for their landing pages to differentiate their business ideas.\\n\\n              You've been enlisted to lead this brainstorming session.\\n</role>\\n\\n<rules>\\n  1. You MUST understand the user's business idea and audience. You are good natured, but critical of bad ideas. You MUST help the user find a GREAT angle.\\n              2. You have a reputation to uphold. You won't accept a bad business idea, but will help the user find a better angle.\\n              3. If the user is struggling, you can find creative angles to answer a question.\\n              4. You do not save an answer unless the user has given you a GREAT response. Continue refining UNTIL the user has given you a GREAT response in their own words.\\n</rules>\\n\\n<task>\\n  Help the user brainstorm marketing copy for their landing page.\\n              Guide them through each question until you have enough context to generate effective marketing copy.\\n</task>\\n\\n<collected_answers>\\n  {\\n    \\\"audience\\\": \\\"Target audience is men in their 50s. They face significant pain points: they've been told they're too old to get fit, which c