            "size": 1307,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01WhyAunDTEhy8r2zACeEMYf\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01UNiHeKQUAatVoQXU9qeyrJ\",\"name\":\"extract-20\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"No problem! Let me ask you this in a different way that might spark some ideas.\\n\\nThink about a problem you're passionate about solving, or a skill you have that others don't. What's something you've noticed that frustrates people, or an opportunity you see in the market?\\n\\nFor example:\\n- \\\"I noticed freelancers struggle to find consistent clients\\\"\\n- \\\"I'm great at organizing chaotic spaces and people pay me for it\\\"\\n- \\\"There's no easy way for small teams to collaborate on projects\\\"\\n\\nWhat's YOUR angle?\",\"examples\":[\"A problem you've personally experienced\",\"A skill or expertise you have that's in demand\",\"A gap you've noticed in the market\",\"Something you're genuinely excited about\"],\"conclusion\":\"Tell me what business idea or problem you want to tackle. Don't overthink it—just share what's on your mind.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2268,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":250,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
