            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01L6Wj2zUWYJC9CL9sby2uRS\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_0159m4uCuh8f99Mf7ahb8pve\",\"name\":\"extract-24\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"Great! So you're building a podcast matchmaking service. I love the concept—but I need to dig deeper to find your real competitive edge.\\n\\nLet me ask you this: **What specific problem are you solving?** Are you matching:\\n- Podcast hosts with potential guests?\\n- Podcasters with collaboration opportunities?\\n- Listeners with shows they'll love?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\nAnd more importantly: **What makes Friend of the Pod different** from just using Twitter, LinkedIn, or existing podcast networks to find connections?\",\"examples\":[\"We match niche podcast hosts with experts in their field who want media exposure\",\"We help independent podcasters find guests who can actually drive their audience growth\",\"We use AI to match hosts and guests based on audience overlap and content alignment\"],\"conclusion\":\"Help me understand the core problem you're solving and what makes your solution unique.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2306,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":247,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
