            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1577,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01MFi8NQiY8ugV6K2TE29maW\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01CURYB7cPY3S2dKK5GsdpuN\",\"name\":\"extract-26\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but let's stay focused! 😄 We're building something great here with Friend of the Pod, and I need your input to make it work.\\\\n\\\\nLet me ask again: **What specific problem does Friend of the Pod solve?** \\\\n\\\\nAre you matching:\\\\n- Podcast hosts with guests?\\\\n- Podcasters with sponsors?\\\\n- Listeners with shows they'll love?\\\\n- Co-hosts with each other?\\\\n- Something completely different?\\\\n\\\\nAnd crucially: **What makes your matchmaking service different** from existing platforms like Podpage, Podmatch, or other guest-booking services?\\\\n\\\\nI need these details to craft compelling marketing copy that'll actually convert your target audience.\",\"examples\":[\"We use AI to match podcast hosts with guests based on audience alignment, not just availability\",\"We connect indie podcasters with micro-sponsors who genuinely care about their niche\",\"We match co-hosts based on chemistry and complementary skills, not just experience\"],\"conclusion\":\"Give me the real story: Who are you connecting, and what makes your approach better than what's already out there?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2769,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":312,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
