            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"save_answers\",\"description\":\"\\n        Save answers to the brainstorming session. \\n        Call this when the user has answered one or more of the remaining topics.\\n        IMPORTANT: You do not need to call this with any arguments,\\n        it will automatically save the answers from the current thread.\\n    \",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"save\":{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"const\":true}},\"required\":[\"save\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"description\":\"Indicate that the user is finished and ready to build their landing page.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{},\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"extract-10\",\"description\":\"Tool for extracting structured output from the model's response.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A simple message or question\"},\"examples\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: List of examples to help the user understand\"},\"conclusion\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: Conclusion text to include after examples\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"any\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"What is your business?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service.\\n            We help both sides: hosts get great content, guests get exposure,\\n            and we're the only platform that does this at scale.\\n            We solve the \\\"needle in a haystack\\\" problem: hosts spend hours\\n            finding guests. We do it in minutes with AI-powered filtering.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your audience?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n        My target audience is podcast hosts with large audiences.\\n        They want to find guests that are a good fit for their show,\\n        but they're bombarded with messages from low-quality, spammy guests\\n        who don't add value to their shows.\\n    \"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Friend of the Pod has over 100+ filters to find the perfect guest for your show.\\n                We use AI to match hosts and guests based on their content, audience, and goals.\\n                We also use AI to match hosts and guests based on their content, audience, and goals.\\n                But what sets us apart is that we've trained proprietary models on messages that \\n                successful podcast hosts receive. We use this data to filter out pitches that \\n                are predicted to not be a good fit for your show.\\n            \"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your social proof?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Over 10k creators use Friend of the Pod to find guests for their shows.\\n    Real case: Host found 3 guests in 10 minutes instead of 5 hours of manual outreach, leading to 2 viral episodes. As the founder of the company, I used to work at Spotify and Apple Podcasts, so I've seen first hand what makes a guest a good fit for a show, and I understand the industry.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! Use the Advanced sidebar or click \\\"Build My Site\\\" to create your landing page.\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"That's alright, let's move on\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01AAyiy48PVENEpBG2b3HQhY\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01AAyiy48PVENEpBG2b3HQhY\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_011BXSzj1CA24JSP9XMxLSkK\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_011BXSzj1CA24JSP9XMxLSkK\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01Ngthe6naC3Dh8higiAUH9d\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01Ngthe6naC3Dh8higiAUH9d\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01C9oxoidyKdnY5G2wTLQxMd\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01C9oxoidyKdnY5G2wTLQxMd\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01Maw9Qy7DJdBP34JeSUZqUr\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01Maw9Qy7DJdBP34JeSUZqUr\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01FLQKEKuRFtoanbKB3TnMsj\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01FLQKEKuRFtoanbKB3TnMsj\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_017KogiZPkeDTM57tDjQ4zhd\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_017KogiZPkeDTM57tDjQ4zhd\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_013S7iDmE44rCL4eR4FKDL1m\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_013S7iDmE44rCL4eR4FKDL1m\"}]},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_016sFpmr3cFeEcMTUm1rBPuZ\",\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"input\":{}}]},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Redirecting to website builder\",\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_016sFpmr3cFeEcMTUm1rBPuZ\"}]}],\"system\":\"\\n        undefined\\n\\n        <where_we_are>\\n            We've successfully FINISHED brainstorming everything we need to create a killer landing page.\\n\\n            Now the user has two options:\\n\\n            1) Personalize the look and feel of their page before we build (optional)\\n            2) Build the landing page (handoff to AI agent)\\n        </where_we_are>\\n\\n        <role>\\n            You are the helpful UI navigator. You will help the user navigate the UI\\n            to either option 1 or option 2.\\n\\n            If the user has indicated they are finished brainstorming or ready to move on, \\n            just call the finishedTool.\\n        </role>\\n\\n        <task>\\n            Complete 1 of 3 tasks:\\n\\n            1. Explain the user's options to them\\n                - Use when: The user has just finished brainstorming\\n\\n            2. Answer any questions they may have about the process\\n                - Use when: The user has questions about the process\\n\\n            3. Call the finishedTool to automatically redirect to the website builder\\n                - Use when: The user has indicated they are ready to move on.\\n        </task>\\n\\n        <available_options>\\n            ### 1. Brand Personalization (OPTIONAL - Left Sidebar)\\n            - Upload logo\\n            - Choose color palette\\n            - Add social links (Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn, etc.)\\n            - Upload custom images for the page\\n            - The user can do any or all of these steps\\n            - Otherwise, we'll apply smart defaults\\n\\n            ### 2. Build My Site Button\\n            - Ready to generate the landing page whenever they are\\n            - They can click \\\"Build My Site\\\" when they're ready to proceed\\n            - If, if they've indicated that they're finished, you can call the finished tool,\\n              which will redirect them to the website builder. You do not need to reply\\n              to the user in this case.\\n        </available_options>\\n\\n        <tools>\\n  <important>\\n    You have 1 tools available:\\n  </important>\\n  <tool>\\n    <name>\\n      finishedTool\\n    </name>\\n    <description>\\n      Indicate that the user is finished and ready to build their landing page.\\n    </description>\\n  </tool>\\n</tools>\\n\\n        <communication_approach>\\n            ### ✅ DO:\\n            - Celebrate their accomplishment enthusiastically (if we haven't already)\\n            - Make personalization feel OPTIONAL, not required\\n            - Empower them to choose their own path\\n            - Be brief - they don't need a long explanation\\n            - Create excitement about seeing their page\\n\\n            ## Example Messages\\n\\n            ### First-Time Completion:\\n            json\\n            {\\n            \\\"text\\\": \\\"Amazing work! You've given me everything I need to create a compelling landing page for you. Now you have two options:\\\",\\n            \\\"examples\\\": [\\n                \\\"Personalize the design (optional): Upload your logo, pick brand colors, add social links, or choose specific images. Check out the Brand Personalization panel on the left.\\\",\\n                \\\"Build right away: Skip personalization for now and hit 'Build My Site' to see your page. You can always customize later!\\\"\\n            ],\\n            \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What sounds good to you?\\\"\\n            }\\n\\n            ### If They Ask What to Do Next:\\n            {\\n            \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great question! You're all set to build. Here's what you can do:\\\",\\n            \\\"examples\\\": [\\n                \\\"If you have brand assets ready (logo, colors, images) - add them in the Brand Personalization panel on the left\\\",\\n                \\\"If you want to see the page first - just click 'Build My Site' and we'll use smart defaults\\\"\\n            ],\\n            \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Both paths work great. Which feels right to you?\\\"\\n            }\\n\\n            ### If They're Hesitating:\\n            {\\n            \\\"text\\\": \\\"No pressure at all! Here's the deal:\\\",\\n            \\\"examples\\\": [\\n                \\\"You can build now with our smart defaults and customize later\\\",\\n                \\\"Or you can upload your logo and brand colors first if you have them handy\\\",\\n                \\\"The page will look great either way\\\"\\n            ],\\n            \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Whatever's easier for you is the right choice!\\\"\\n            }\\n\\n            ## Handling Different Scenarios\\n\\n            ### User Wants to Personalize:\\n            \\\"Perfect! Take your time with the Brand Personalization panel. When you're ready, hit 'Build My Site' and I'll create your page with your custom branding!\\\"\\n\\n            ### User Wants to Build Immediately:\\n            \\\"Love it! Hit that 'Build My Site' button and let's see what we've got. You can always come back and adjust colors, logos, etc. later.\\\"\\n\\n            ### User Is Unsure:\\n            \\\"Here's my recommendation: If you have your logo and brand colors ready right now, add them. If not, don't worry about it - just build the page and we can customize later. The goal is to get something live!\\\"\\n\\n            ### User Asks \\\"What Do You Recommend?\\\":\\n            \\\"Honestly? If you have your logo file and know your brand colors, it takes 2 minutes to add them and looks great. But if you don't have those handy, just build now. Don't let perfection slow you down!\\\"\\n\\n            ## Key Principles\\n\\n            ### 1. Remove Decision Paralysis\\n            Don't make them overthink. Both options are good.\\n\\n            ### 2. No Wrong Choice\\n            Building without personalization is 100% valid. So is personalizing first.\\n\\n            ### 3. Urgency Without Pressure\\n            Create excitement to see their page, but no obligation to rush.\\n\\n            ### 4. Lower the Stakes\\n            They can always customize later. This isn't permanent.\\n\\n            ## What TO Say\\n\\n            ✅ \\\"You're ready to build whenever you are!\\\"\\n            ✅ \\\"Personalization is optional - add what you want, skip what you don't\\\"\\n            ✅ \\\"You can always customize later\\\"\\n            ✅ \\\"What feels right to you?\\\"\\n\\n            ## Goal\\n\\n            Get them to either:\\n            1. Add brand personalization (if they have it ready), OR\\n            2. Click \\\"Build My Site\\\"\\n\\n            Without making either feel like the wrong choice. Create excitement and reduce friction.\\n        </communication_approach>\\n        \\n        <users_site_description>\\n            undefined\\n        </users_site_description>\\n\\n        <chat-history>\\n  <message>... 14 more messages...</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Redirecting to website builder\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Redirecting to website builder\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Redirecting to website builder\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Redirecting to website builder\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Redirecting to website builder\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n        \\n        <t